Privacy Policy for BetterStats

Effective Date: 18.20.2024

At BetterStats, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our bot.
1. Data Collection

    User Data: BetterStats collects only the data that you provide when using the bot. This may include your Discord ID, username, and any other relevant information necessary to provide you with the requested services.

2. Data Usage

    Temporary Storage: All user data collected by BetterStats is stored temporarily. We retain your data only for as long as necessary to fulfill your requests and provide you with our services.

    Data Access: Your data is accessed solely when you make a request through the bot. We do not retain or store your data beyond the required time to process your request.

3. Data Sharing

    No Third-Party Sharing: BetterStats does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. Your data will not be shared with any external entities without your explicit consent, unless required by law.

4. Data Security

    We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

    We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and the effective date will be updated. Your continued use of BetterStats after any changes signifies your acceptance of the updated policy.

6. Contact

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at Astro-Development67@gmx.de
